Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.38,0:00:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know there's an awesome\Ntreasure at the end of this sea?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.61,0:00:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And whoever gets it can be King\Nof the Pirates! Isn't that exciting?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.18,0:00:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unheard-of adventures are waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.39,0:00:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bon voyage! Let that shred of courage grow
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.26,0:00:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I caught a glimpse of\Nthe tail end to the future
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.90,0:00:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The horizons everyone\Ndreamed of were separate at first
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.68,0:00:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but now they can be seen\Nthrough a single telescope
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.82,0:00:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A bitter compass of destiny\Nis leading your heart astray
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.16,0:00:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so turn the wheel in the other direction!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.06,0:01:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bon voyage!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.13,0:01:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Toss aside your bonds and your past
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.37,0:01:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can surely smile despite that
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.38,0:01:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tears shed trying to achieve\Nyour dreams aren't for naught
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.86,0:01:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Precious in my life
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.26,0:01:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I caught a glimpse of\Nthe tail end to the future
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.14,0:01:40.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure it was right around here...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.71,0:01:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.18,0:01:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If things are going as planned,\NLuffy and the others
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.58,0:01:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,should be headed back to\Nthe dock with our gold in hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.71,0:01:51.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, I really did forget about this!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.55,0:01:56.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't realize it before, but this\NWaver works in the Blue Sea, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.16,0:01:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Now we just gotta hurry back!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.79,0:02:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji-kun! Hold on tight!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.56,0:02:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onto you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.86,0:02:06.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad I'm alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.23,0:02:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God! Buddha! I thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.63,0:02:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah, whatever. Just get on already!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.57,0:02:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mind if I do, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.81,0:02:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You moron! I can't move like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.01,0:02:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your expressions of love are dynamic!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.68,0:02:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I collapse and literally fall in love...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.78,0:02:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.35,0:02:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.03,0:02:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The One Fell Swoop Plan!\NJonathan's Surefire Secret Tactic"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.50,0:02:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like we've been had...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.37,0:02:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to hand it to them...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.91,0:02:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna catch a fish that big!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.68,0:02:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you be so carefree after\Nwe nearly died trying to open it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.45,0:02:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our commander said you would appear here,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.85,0:02:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,since you had stolen the map.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.88,0:03:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cunning man.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.09,0:03:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is nowhere to run now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.22,0:03:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! As strong as Luffy and Zoro are...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.42,0:03:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do we wait for Sanji and the others\Nto break through from outside?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.56,0:03:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.66,0:03:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our actions should already be known by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.60,0:03:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's only a matter of time\Nuntil reinforcements arrive.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.90,0:03:18.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no use in staying here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.20,0:03:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! If the gold's not here,\Nthen let's just go look somewhere else!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.24,0:03:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk like it's so easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.31,0:03:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only way out is to beat these guys
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.51,0:03:30.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and bust down those sturdy doors!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.55,0:03:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.92,0:03:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly! We gotta do what we gotta do!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.99,0:03:40.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the name of Navarone, we will defeat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.09,0:03:48.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp's in trouble!\NHe's helpless to do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.34,0:03:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,End of the line, Straw Hats!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.61,0:03:55.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Huh?\N--Condoriano?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.24,0:03:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You came to the storage vault,\Nexactly as I expected!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.34,0:04:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell are you?! Who gave\Nyou permission to open the doors?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.75,0:04:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quiet, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.98,0:04:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am a special inspector\Nfrom Navy HQ, Major Shepherd!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.25,0:04:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With the commander's permission,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.76,0:04:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am leading a special\Nmobile unit from headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.66,0:04:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are not needed. Step back!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.73,0:04:21.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Haven't I seen you somewhere before?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.83,0:04:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah! You were the guy\Nin jail with Usopp and Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.87,0:04:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you to talk all big?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.04,0:04:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Condoriano! You managed to escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.98,0:04:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem well!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.75,0:04:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I owe a great deal to you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.45,0:04:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the insults you've put me through...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.99,0:04:46.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's payback time for that, with interest!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.86,0:04:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Major Shepherd!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.53,0:04:50.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Things were just getting good!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.73,0:04:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taking them down with that level\Nof military might is impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.43,0:04:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't underestimate them...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.14,0:04:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, shut up, shut up! Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.54,0:05:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't compare us HQ elites\Nwith you pathetic Navarone men!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.31,0:05:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will eliminate the Straw Hats!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.78,0:05:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just sit there and watch! Is that clear?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.55,0:05:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.48,0:05:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you done?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.49,0:05:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! I'm gonna crush you good,\Nso stay right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.92,0:05:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Bring it here!\N--Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.03,0:05:21.61,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Justice"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.63,0:05:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.06,0:05:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Navy HQ's very latest\Ninvention: a portable bazooka!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.47,0:05:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Sea Eagle Talon-- the Eagle Launcher!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.04,0:05:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It packs as much punch\Nas a warship's main cannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.57,0:05:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.67,0:05:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They've brought out another incredible thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.78,0:05:38.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't scare me! Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.94,0:05:46.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll fulfill that request! Time to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.15,0:05:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Huh?\N--Way to go, Condoriano!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.82,0:05:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Major! You have it backwards!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.56,0:05:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--O-Oh.\N--Hey, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.09,0:06:03.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! I'll get you this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.74,0:06:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! No! Don't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.65,0:06:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Way to go, Condoriano!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.21,0:06:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell'd he come here to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.95,0:06:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's pretty disappointing\Nfor a "special mobile unit."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.75,0:06:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then. Shall we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.66,0:06:27.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Gold! Gold!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.13,0:06:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Wait, you guys! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.16,0:06:32.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Damn you, Straw Hats! I'll get you--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.87,0:06:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My bad, Condoriano!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.17,0:06:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let them escape! After them!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.27,0:06:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--So, where's the gold now?\N--Don't look at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.48,0:06:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Security's tighter than I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.78,0:06:54.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All alone with Nami-san\Non a romantic night at sea...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.09,0:06:56.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Isn't it the damn greatest, Nami-san?!\N--Sanji-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.99,0:06:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Damn bravo, Nami-san!\N--Sanji-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.73,0:07:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're damn fantastic, Nami-san!\NIt's bon voyage, Nami--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.13,0:07:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji-kun! Could you be damn quiet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.73,0:07:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This means the Navy is certain\Nwe're still inside the base.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.87,0:07:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But then why are they just\Nsitting there? I don't like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.74,0:07:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's rethink our plan somewhere safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.71,0:07:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there any safe place here on Navarone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.58,0:07:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! The kitchen me and Sanji were at!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.12,0:07:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's where loads of marines gather to eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.52,0:07:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't go someplace that dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.32,0:07:32.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, wait. The enemy might\Nthink the same thing, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.86,0:07:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! It's decided! Let's go get some food!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.49,0:07:37.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what we're doing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.73,0:07:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a full-fledged pirate now! I've grown a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.93,0:07:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll protect it, no matter\Nwho comes! I'm a reliable man!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.91,0:07:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.14,0:07:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami! Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.34,0:07:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're all right! I wasn't\Nlonely at all, you dummies!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.91,0:07:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are Luffy and the rest not back yet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.52,0:07:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope! I've been keeping watch all alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.28,0:08:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.62,0:08:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something might've happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.22,0:08:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Then, the gold, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.22,0:08:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Yeah.\N--I'm gonna go look!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.73,0:08:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My date with Nami-san, Part 2!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.29,0:08:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All alone again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.56,0:08:13.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You stay here, too, Sanji-kun.\N--Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.23,0:08:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a favor to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.97,0:08:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty sure the vault\Nwas down here somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.51,0:08:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.14,0:08:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Straw Hats fled into\Nthe mountains! Comb the hills!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.78,0:08:32.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry! No dawdling!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.95,0:08:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right, Major Shepherd?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.19,0:08:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! I almost had them, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.82,0:08:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But finding an empty vault doesn't\Nmean they'll give up just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.66,0:08:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We still have a chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.83,0:08:48.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Empty?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.20,0:08:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I figured this might happen,\Nso the next step is already set.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.94,0:08:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I always know what I'm doing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.71,0:09:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The vault was a trap! Then where is the gold?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.80,0:09:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it was around here...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.00,0:09:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, now. Come on already...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.77,0:09:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.60,0:09:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you just there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.30,0:09:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The dining hall is at the far end.\NThis is the medical ward.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.41,0:09:34.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like there's someone here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.18,0:09:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad! Please do as I ask!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.88,0:09:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care if you are my daughter;\NI refuse to drink that nasty stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.89,0:09:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's medicine!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.82,0:09:43.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those voices...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.19,0:09:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the doctor who acted as a hostage...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.89,0:09:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and the old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.03,0:09:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The gold wasn't on your ship?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.10,0:09:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nor in the vault.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.93,0:09:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, I can't believe\Nyou're father and daughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.73,0:09:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, old man, are you sick or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.20,0:10:02.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, just one swig of this\Nand I'll sleep it off like a baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.21,0:10:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a much better medicine for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.91,0:10:09.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! There is no drinking or\Nsmoking in the medical ward!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.11,0:10:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Just one drink!\N--No!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.08,0:10:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so stubborn...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.92,0:10:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Old man! You need to listen to\Nyour daughter-- no, your doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.02,0:10:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this? Are you trying to lecture me now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.39,0:10:24.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I save your hides, and you\Ncome waltzing right back...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.16,0:10:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want your gold that badly, Long-nose?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.50,0:10:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course we do, old repair guy! We're pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.34,0:10:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! These pirates worked\Nreally hard to get their stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.34,0:10:39.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You keep out of this, Kobato!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.18,0:10:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're saving up money!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.88,0:10:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saving?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.05,0:10:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We decided that after we\Nexchange the gold for money,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.88,0:10:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we're gonna do major repairs on Merry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.82,0:10:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like we can really believe a bunch of pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.52,0:10:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care if you don't believe me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.89,0:10:55.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This was our decision!\NIt's got nothing to do with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.53,0:10:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.96,0:10:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.43,0:11:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all... they said that ship was their home.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.34,0:11:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Home, indeed...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.44,0:11:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is it! It's a bit of a long way around,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.11,0:11:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but this path is unguarded, and it'll\Ntake you safely to the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.62,0:11:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This "path" is almost all cliff!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.99,0:11:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, then! Let's go\Ngold-hunting! Thanks, old guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.22,0:11:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Sure thing!\N--Get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.86,0:11:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for your help again, old man! See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.73,0:11:32.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Wait!\N--What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.50,0:11:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our commander's hobby is fishing, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.60,0:11:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that explains why he showed\Noff that huge fish painting!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.17,0:11:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your gold is probably the\Nperfect bait to reel you in with.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.01,0:11:47.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In which case, it should be\Ndangling somewhere you can see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.98,0:11:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someplace we can see it? Bait?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.95,0:11:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hurry up!\N--Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.59,0:11:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Now get going!\N--Right! See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.02,0:11:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.16,0:12:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they do steal back the gold\Nand manage to escape,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.33,0:12:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,all of Navarone will be in big trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.16,0:12:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must be crazy...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.07,0:12:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was no time to think up\Na plan after all, was there?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.57,0:12:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! Are we left to\Nlook around aimlessly for it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.74,0:12:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Zoro?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.35,0:12:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thought I heard something...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.72,0:12:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A bug? Must be my imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.92,0:12:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it isn't your imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.29,0:12:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.63,0:12:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Waver?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.29,0:12:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.73,0:12:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So you ran into Dr. Kobato...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.03,0:12:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We pretty much have no clues\Nabout where the gold is!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.84,0:12:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sleepy...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.57,0:12:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we sit around and dawdle,\Ndawn's gonna come,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.88,0:12:54.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which'll make it even harder to move around.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.71,0:12:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, are there any other storage vaults?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.02,0:13:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If there are, they could be\Ntraps to lure us in again...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.62,0:13:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, the old man\Nsaid something earlier about "bait"...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.96,0:13:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? What do you mean by "something"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.66,0:13:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not really sure, but he said...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.13,0:13:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it! Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.37,0:13:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.67,0:13:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bait to reel us in... In other words,\Nthe gold is somewhere in sight!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.88,0:13:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In sight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.91,0:13:28.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could "sight" be referring to a\Nplace we could imagine it being?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.75,0:13:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, good thinking!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.45,0:13:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.68,0:13:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In short, who's the one dangling\Nthe bait to catch us in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.29,0:13:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Navarone's commander?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.79,0:13:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Navarone's commander is the fisherman.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.03,0:13:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if the bait is near the fisherman,\Nthere's only one place it could be.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.13,0:13:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't mean--!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.24,0:13:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.17,0:13:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.21,0:13:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said you know where the\Ncommander's room is, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.01,0:13:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lead us there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.64,0:14:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.38,0:14:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Luffy and I will go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.95,0:14:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin and the rest, get to the coast!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.82,0:14:07.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper's group should come to get you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.45,0:14:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you be all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.92,0:14:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Waver can only hold two people.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.43,0:14:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we're gonna get spotted\Nanyway, so it doesn't matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.46,0:14:23.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna run it at full throttle! You ready?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.07,0:14:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Anytime you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.20,0:14:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.28,0:14:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They've appeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.71,0:14:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.95,0:14:40.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.09,0:14:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and find it, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.59,0:14:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Up! Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.25,0:14:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Up where, exactly?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.82,0:14:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let them escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.83,0:14:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.96,0:14:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.80,0:14:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a surprise this is!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.97,0:15:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that vehicle?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.04,0:15:05.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he the commander?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.98,0:15:07.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, he's the old fortress guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.98,0:15:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never imagined you would\Nmake an entrance through there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.32,0:15:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cool, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.99,0:15:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is actually a vehicle from the sky!\NOnly Nami can ride it, though!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.02,0:15:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Quit getting excited!\N--Yes! I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.86,0:15:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've not met this girl before. Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.53,0:15:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you not pirates, I'd greet you\Nwarmly for your boisterous visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.53,0:15:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a real shame. You're perceptive and bold.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.80,0:15:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But daring can also sometimes\Nbe called recklessness.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.94,0:15:42.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There will be no soldiers coming\Nto eat this time, Straw Hat Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.48,0:15:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But first! If there's no bait,\Nwe have nothing to bite onto!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.35,0:15:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the gold?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.92,0:15:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hidden in this room, isn't it?\NCouldn't you at least show it to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.36,0:15:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. It's right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.23,0:15:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right in front of me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.10,0:16:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, here it is! The gold!\NNami! We finally found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.20,0:16:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not fake bait, I hope?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.50,0:16:08.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's indeed the genuine article.\NCheck for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.44,0:16:10.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Okay, then!\N--Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.54,0:16:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.28,0:16:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is our gold, no doubt about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.08,0:16:20.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Let's go now! Sorry for\Nthe intrusion, old fortress guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.55,0:16:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoops, I think not.\NYou can't just take the bait and run.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.29,0:16:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try not to be too rough with the lady, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.33,0:16:32.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.86,0:16:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat comes first.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.87,0:16:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll beat the whole lot of you up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.60,0:16:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Another weird net... I'm out of strength...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.68,0:16:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sea Prism Stone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.88,0:16:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat is captured!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.38,0:16:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excellent work. Now, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.28,0:16:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not good! What do I do?!\NThere's gotta be something!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.12,0:16:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, if these guys have guns,\NI do have a chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.59,0:16:59.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rain Tempo! Sprinkler!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.69,0:17:01.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cool Ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.59,0:17:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.59,0:17:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heat Ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.50,0:17:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's warm...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.16,0:17:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I did it!\N--W-What the--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.27,0:17:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A cloud?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.57,0:17:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today's forecast calls for\Nclear skies and 0% chance of rain!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.97,0:17:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But cumulonimbus clouds may\Nsuddenly develop in some places!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.18,0:17:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please watch out for lightning!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.14,0:17:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this, Miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.61,0:17:30.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thunderbolt Tempo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.56,0:17:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.66,0:17:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.13,0:17:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pull yourself together!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.63,0:17:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Nami...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.13,0:17:49.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry! Grab our gold!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.21,0:17:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not one to let prey escape\Nafter hooking it once before...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.41,0:18:00.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll catch all of you in one fell swoop.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.45,0:18:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Luffy?! See the ship?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.02,0:18:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too dark to see anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.49,0:18:13.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look out, Nami! A navy ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.60,0:18:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, it does look kind of like a warship...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.94,0:18:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There they are! Over here, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.04,0:18:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.28,0:18:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san! Are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.35,0:18:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just let Straw Hats who\Nwere in your own room get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.69,0:18:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They even stole the gold. Even you\Nmust admit this is a grave failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.32,0:18:44.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They will not escape my\Nclutches, Major Shepherd.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.33,0:18:47.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You still won't admit defeat,\Nafter all that's happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.93,0:18:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I apologize. What do you say, Commander?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.90,0:18:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you sit there quietly\Nand observe my leadership skills?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.31,0:18:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you had already had enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.38,0:19:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened earlier was\Nsimply a minor complication!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.41,0:19:03.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had already sent out my\Nspecial pirate subjugation squad,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.41,0:19:05.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,separate from my main unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.05,0:19:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. Then I think I will sit back\Nand watch you in action.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.39,0:19:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the captain of the Pinepeak?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.19,0:19:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They will appear near the Sea Gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.73,0:19:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as planned, wait for them\Nto get drawn to it, then sink 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.46,0:19:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Got that?!\N--Understood, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.03,0:19:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain! We're about to\Nreach the ambush point!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.00,0:19:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Do not let the pirate ship slip by!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.80,0:19:29.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The minute it's spotted,\Ncommence a full-scale attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.64,0:19:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That takes care of all the preparations.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.64,0:19:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now to watch things from a high\Nvantage point. Place a pole in--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.05,0:19:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you please not touch that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.29,0:19:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May I ask you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.79,0:19:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-If it's about how to catch pirates,\NI can teach you anytime you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.19,0:19:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't this special squadron\Nof yours on the Pinepeak?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.26,0:19:55.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There seems to be one more ship...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.53,0:19:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say what?! T-That can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.80,0:20:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's no Navarone warship.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.07,0:20:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it doesn't even look like it is a warship.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.31,0:20:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.58,0:20:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.08,0:20:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A warship-- no, a warship-like ship--\Nis approaching from behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.35,0:20:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Navarone ship?\NAnd what do you mean, "like"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.82,0:20:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm not really sure how to answer...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.16,0:20:23.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's going to smash into us!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.13,0:20:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.70,0:20:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Full speed ahead, Merry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.57,0:20:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What the--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.87,0:20:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the piloting! Couldn't\Nhave made it this far without you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.71,0:20:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks a bunch! We owe ya one!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.95,0:20:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let them escape! After them!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.68,0:20:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is no time for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.65,0:20:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.76,0:20:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Impossible! To think they'd\Nuse the Pinepeak, of all things!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.33,0:20:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you, you Straw Hats!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.70,0:21:03.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so aggravated.\NThey're as good as caught in a net now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.53,0:21:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Net?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.00,0:21:08.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At 9:00 pm, the waters of\NNavarone bare their fangs,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.44,0:21:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the final-- and inescapable-- trap begins!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.28,0:21:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Now we can escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.72,0:21:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus we got the gold!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.39,0:21:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We did it! We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.09,0:21:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Let's rush straight to the Sea Gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.39,0:21:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.31,0:21:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and get moving towards the future!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.65,0:22:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's move ahead, pursuing our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.50,0:22:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the answers are right here, pouring out
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.51,0:22:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rush forth, rush forth,\Non the road opened before us
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.68,0:22:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's keep moving forward! We can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.25,0:22:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't give in, we won't give in,\Neven if the obstacle is big
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.46,0:22:43.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing to be scared of,\Nwe can overcome it
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.21,0:22:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attention, Straw Hat Luffy and his crew!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.05,0:23:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've fought most valiantly against\Nthe Navy's great G8 Fortress!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.32,0:23:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've done admirably, but this is the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.16,0:23:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Just give it up, Straw Hats!\N--We still have a chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.66,0:23:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.90,0:23:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Farewell, Navy Fortress!\NThe Last Battle for Escape"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.37,0:23:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
